          <title>The Bay Area's Modest Job Gains Outshine California's Slump</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Bay Area managed modest job gains in November, but more than half of them were in the East Bay as the tech-heavy South Bay and San Francisco metro region lagged by a wide margin, according to a report from the state's labor agency.]]></description>
